[0m[49m[39m  179, 151[0m:[39m[49m ### Ingredients
[0m[49m[39m  180, 152[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  181, 153[0m:[39m[49m | AWS Service | Role |
[0m[49m[39m  182, 154[0m:[39m[49m |------------|------|
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 183     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Amazon Comprehend Medical (InferICD10CM)** | Takes clinical text, returns ranked ICD-10-CM codes with confidence scores and evidence text spans |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 184     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Amazon Comprehend Medical (DetectEntitiesV2)** | Extracts clinical entities with assertion traits (negation, temporality) for evidence and filtering |
